Lalanirina Rosa Rakotozafy (amụrụ na onwa12 Nọvemba , na afọ 1977) bụ onye na-eme egwuregwu na Madagascar bụ ọkachamara na 100 mita hurdles.
Oge kachasị mma ya bụ 12.84 sekọnd, nke o nwetara na Julai, na afọ 1999 na Niort
Nke a bụ ihe ndekọ Malagasy ugbu a
O jikwa ihe ndekọ mita 200 nke mba na 23.09 sekọnd.
